{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775890277605,"sessionID":"ses_284b12e61ffegKYv9ZTZvGCjkO","part":{"id":"prt_d7b4f1fd10012U1x6rqD77dSyP","messageID":"msg_d7b4f0563001w9TmbiWSILQ3pB","sessionID":"ses_284b12e61ffegKYv9ZTZvGCjkO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_e9d9571fe1964972b44c8bec","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## 1. Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，确保代码质量、可维护性和可靠性。\n6: \n7: 本提案针对 AR-039 需求，覆盖以下核心组件：\n8: - **Router**: 路由管理、反向代理、健康检查、JWT 认证\n9: - **Store**: Redis/Valkey 存储后端、会话管理、过期/ inactive 清理\n10: - **PicoD**: 沙箱执行器、文件系统、资源限制、安全选项\n11: \n12: ## 2. Scope\n13: \n14: ### 2.1 In Scope\n15: \n16: | 模块 | 文件 | 优先级 | 测试类型 | 当前状态 |\n17: |------|------|--------|----------|----------|\n18: | **pkg/router** | | | | |\n19: | | `router.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 部分覆盖 |\n20: | | `handler.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 部分覆盖 |\n21: | | `resolver.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n22: | | `health.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n23: | | `session_handler.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n24: | | `session_resolver.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n25: | | `config.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n26: | | `types.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n27: | | `handlers/token.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n28: | | `handlers/refresh.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n29: | | `handlers/revoke.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n30: | | `middleware/auth.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n31: | | `middleware/session_middleware.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n32: | | `blacklist/blacklist.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n33: | | `auth/jwt.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 需要补充 |\n34: | **pkg/store** | | | | |\n35: | | `store.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 部分覆盖 |\n36: | | `store_redis.go` | P0 | 单元测试 + mock | 已有测试 |\n37: | | `store_valkey.go` | P0 | 单元测试 + mock | 已有测试 |\n38: | | `codec.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n39: | | `singleton.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n40: | **pkg/picod** | | | | |\n41: | | `picod.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n42: | | `executor.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n43: | | `filesystem.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n44: | | `config.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n45: | | `jwt.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n46: | | `middleware.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n47: | | `security.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n48: | | `limits.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n49: | | `quota.go` | P1 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n50: | | `process.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n51: | | `output.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n52: | | `path.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n53: | | `fileinfo.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n54: | | `errors.go` | P2 | 单元测试 | 已有测试 |\n55: \n56: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n57: \n58: - E2E 测试（由单独的测试计划覆盖）\n59: - 性能/负载测试\n60: - Valkey 集成测试（已有 `store_valkey_integration_test.go`）\n61: - PicoD 集成测试（已有 `integration_test.go`）\n62: \n63: ## 3. Impact Analysis\n64: \n65: ### 3.1 代码依赖\n66: \n67: ```\n68: pkg/router/\n69: ├── router.go              → 依赖 k8s client-go, informer, cache\n70: ├── handler.go             → 依赖 httputil, handlers\n71: ├── resolver.go            → 依赖 url parsing, routes\n72: ├── health.go              → 依赖 http client\n73: ├── session_handler.go     → 依赖 http\n74: ├── session_resolver.go    → 依赖 cache, informer\n75: ├── config.go              → 依赖 rest.Config\n76: ├── types.go               → 纯数据类型\n77: ├── handlers/\n78: │   ├── token.go           → 依赖 auth.JWTAuthenticator\n79: │   ├── refresh.go         → 依赖 auth.JWTAuthenticator\n80: │   └── revoke.go          → 依赖 auth.JWTAuthenticator\n81: ├── middleware/\n82: │   ├── auth.go            → 依赖 auth\n83: │   └── session_middleware.go → 依赖 http\n84: ├── blacklist/\n85: │   └── blacklist.go       → 纯工具，已有测试\n86: └── auth/\n87:     └── jwt.go             → 依赖 golang-jwt/jwt/v5\n88: \n89: pkg/store/\n90: ├── store.go               → 接口定义\n91: ├── store_redis.go         → 依赖 go-redis/v9\n92: ├── store_valkey.go        → 依赖 go-redis/v9\n93: ├── codec.go               → 纯工具函数\n94: └── singleton.go           → 依赖 store interface\n95: \n96: pkg/picod/\n97: ├── picod.go               → 依赖 executor, filesystem\n98: ├── executor.go            → 依赖 os/exec, context\n99: ├── filesystem.go          → 依赖 os, io/fs\n100: ├── config.go              → 依赖 encoding/json\n101: ├── jwt.go                 → 依赖 golang-jwt/jwt/v5\n102: ├── middleware.go          → 依赖 http\n103: ├── security.go            → 依赖 os/exec\n104: ├── limits.go              → 依赖 syscall\n105: ├── quota.go               → 依赖 os\n106: ├── process.go             → 依赖 os/exec\n107: ├── output.go              → 纯工具函数\n108: ├── path.go                → 依赖 filepath\n109: ├── fileinfo.go            → 依赖 io/fs\n110: └── errors.go              → 纯工具函数\n111: ```\n112: \n113: ### 3.2 测试基础设施需求\n114: \n115: 1. **Router 测试**:\n116:    - Mock kubernetes client 和 informer\n117:    - Mock HTTP server/client\n118:    - Mock JWT authenticator\n119:    - Test fixtures for RouteEntry, HealthStatus\n120: \n121: 2. **Store 测试**:\n122:    - Mock Redis client (使用 go-redis 的 Mock 或 mock 库)\n123:    - Test fixtures for SandboxInfo\n124: \n125: 3. **PicoD 测试**:\n126:    - 已有多数测试覆盖\n127:    - 需要补充边缘场景测试\n128: \n129: ### 3.3 预期工作量\n130: \n131: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估时间 |\n132: |------|------|----------|\n133: | Phase 1 | Router 核心：router.go, handler.go | 8h |\n134: | Phase 2 | Router 扩展：resolver.go, health.go, session_*.go | 6h |\n135: | Phase 3 | Router Handlers: token.go, refresh.go, revoke.go | 4h |\n136: | Phase 4 | Router Auth/Middleware: auth/jwt.go, middleware/*.go | 4h |\n137: | Phase 5 | Store: store_redis.go, store_valkey.go (mock) | 6h |\n138: | Phase 6 | PicoD 补充测试：executor.go, security.go, limits.go | 4h |\n139: | Phase 7 | 集成测试 + 覆盖率分析 | 4h |\n140: | **总计** | | **36h** |\n141: \n142: ## 4. Alternatives Considered\n143: \n144: ### 4.1 方案 A: 使用 Mock 框架 (推荐用于 Store)\n145: \n146: **描述**: 使用 `gomock` 或 `testify/mock` 为 Redis client 和 kubernetes informer 生成 mock 实现\n147: \n148: **优点**:\n149: - 灵活控制返回值和行为\n150: - 可验证调用顺序和次数\n151: - 无需真实连接 Redis/K8s\n152: \n153: **缺点**:\n154: - 需要维护 mock 代码\n155: - mock 行为可能与真实实现不一致\n156: \n157: **采用原因**: Store 层需要 mock Redis client；Router 需要 mock informer\n158: \n159: ### 4.2 方案 B: 使用 Fake Clients (推荐用于 Router)\n160: \n161: **描述**: 使用 kubernetes client-go 提供的 fake clientset 和 informer\n162: \n163: **优点**:\n164: - 与真实 client 行为一致\n165: - 官方支持，无需额外依赖\n166: - 支持 informer/cache 相关测试\n167: \n168: **缺点**:\n169: - 部分场景需要手动管理 indexer\n170: - 无法模拟所有 API server 错误场景\n171: \n172: **采用原因**: Router 依赖 k8s informer，使用 fake clients 是社区标准做法\n173: \n174: ### 4.3 方案 C: 使用 Testcontainers (可选用于集成测试)\n175: \n176: **描述**: 使用 testcontainers-go 启动真实的 Redis 容器进行测试\n177: \n178: **优点**:\n179: - 最接近真实环境\n180: - 可测试真实 Redis 行为\n181: \n182: **缺点**:\n183: - 测试执行慢（需要启动容器）\n184: - 依赖 Docker\n185: - 不适合快速迭代的单元测试\n186: \n187: **不采用原因**: 已有 `store_valkey_integration_test.go` 覆盖集成测试场景\n188: \n189: ## 5. Test Strategy\n190: \n191: ### 5.1 测试分层\n192: \n193: ```\n194: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n195: │      Integration Tests              │  ← testcontainers (可选)\n196: ├─────────────────────────────────────┤\n197: │    Unit Tests (Fake Clients)        │  ← Router 主要测试层\n198: ├─────────────────────────────────────┤\n199: │    Unit Tests (Mock Clients)        │  ← Store 主要测试层\n200: ├─────────────────────────────────────┤\n201: │    Unit Tests (Pure Functions)      │  ← PicoD 基础测试\n202: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n203: ```\n204: \n205: ### 5.2 覆盖率目标\n206: \n207: - **Line Coverage**: ≥ 80%\n208: - **Branch Coverage**: ≥ 70%\n209: - **核心模块** (router/*, store/*): ≥ 85%\n210: \n211: ### 5.3 测试命名规范\n212: \n213: ```go\n214: // 格式：Test[FunctionName][Scenario]_[ExpectedResult]\n215: func TestRouter_NewRouter_NilConfig_ReturnsError(t *testing.T)\n216: func TestHandler_ServeHTTP_AuthRequired_NoToken_Returns401(t *testing.T)\n217: func TestRedisStore_StoreSandbox_NilSandbox_ReturnsError(t *testing.T)\n218: func TestExecutor_Run_CommandNotFound_ReturnsExecutionError(t *testing.T)\n219: ```\n220: \n221: ### 5.4 表驱动测试模板\n222: \n223: ```go\n224: func TestXxx(t *testing.T) {\n225:     tests := []struct {\n226:         name        string\n227:         input       InputType\n228:         expected    ExpectedType\n229:         expectError bool\n230:     }{\n231:         {\"scenario1\", input1, expected1, false},\n232:         {\"scenario2\", input2, expected2, true},\n233:     }\n234:     \n235:     for _, tt := range tests {\n236:         t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n237:             // test logic\n238:         })\n239:     }\n240: }\n241: ```\n242: \n243: ## 6. Test Cases Detail\n244: \n245: ### 6.1 pkg/router/router.go (P0)\n246: \n247: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n248: |-----------|----------|\n249: | `NewRouter()` | nil config, invalid kubeconfig, success |\n250: | `SetInformers()` | nil informers, valid informers, event handler registration |\n251: | `onAgentRuntimeAdd()` | not exposed, no backend URL, valid add |\n252: | `onAgentRuntimeUpdate()` | update triggers add logic |\n253: | `onAgentRuntimeDelete()` | direct delete, tombstone delete, invalid object |\n254: | `onCodeInterpreter*()` | similar to AgentRuntime |\n255: | `shouldExpose()` | label present/absent/false |\n256: | `extractBackendURLFromStatus()` | nil ref, empty name, valid ref |\n257: | `Start()` | server startup, error handling |\n258: | `Shutdown()` | graceful shutdown, token blacklist stop |\n259: | `GetRoute()` | found, not found |\n260: | `ListRoutes()` | empty, multiple routes |\n261: | `AddRoute()` / `RemoveRoute()` | add/remove operations |\n262: \n263: ### 6.2 pkg/router/handler.go (P0)\n264: \n265: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n266: |-----------|----------|\n267: | `NewHandler()` | with/without auth |\n268: | `ServeHTTP()` | auth endpoints, regular proxy |\n269: | `ProxyRequest()` | valid backend, invalid URL, error handler |\n270: | `AddForwardingHeaders()` | with/without TLS, client IP extraction |\n271: | `writeError()` | various error types, status codes |\n272: \n273: ### 6.3 pkg/router/resolver.go (P1)\n274: \n275: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n276: |-----------|----------|\n277: | `NewResolver()` | initialization |\n278: | `Resolve()` | exact match, prefix match, not found |\n279: | Invalid resource type, malformed path |\n280: \n281: ### 6.4 pkg/router/health.go (P1)\n282: \n283: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n284: |-----------|----------|\n285: | `NewHealthChecker()` | initialization |\n286: | `Start()` / `Stop()` | lifecycle |\n287: | `checkHealth()` | healthy, unhealthy, timeout |\n288: | `tick()` | single check |\n289: \n290: ### 6.5 pkg/router/session_handler.go (P1)\n291: \n292: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n293: |-----------|----------|\n294: | `ServeHTTP()` | session lookup, proxy |\n295: \n296: ### 6.6 pkg/router/session_resolver.go (P1)\n297: \n298: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n299: |-----------|----------|\n300: | `Resolve()` | informer-based resolution |\n301: \n302: ### 6.7 pkg/router/handlers/*.go (P1)\n303: \n304: | 文件 | 测试场景 |\n305: |------|----------|\n306: | `token.go` | valid request, invalid credentials, missing fields |\n307: | `refresh.go` | valid refresh, expired token, invalid token |\n308: | `revoke.go` | valid revoke, missing token |\n309: \n310: ### 6.8 pkg/router/auth/jwt.go (P1)\n311: \n312: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n313: |-----------|----------|\n314: | `NewJWTAuthenticator()` | valid/invalid config |\n315: | `Authenticate()` | valid token, expired, invalid signature |\n316: | `GenerateToken()` / `RefreshToken()` / `RevokeToken()` | respective operations |\n317: \n318: ### 6.9 pkg/store/store_redis.go (P0)\n319: \n320: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n321: |-----------|----------|\n322: | `makeRedisOptions()` | missing env, password required/not required |\n323: | `NewRedisStore()` | initialization |\n324: | `Ping()` | success, failure |\n325: | `GetSandboxBySessionID()` | found, not found, error |\n326: | `StoreSandbox()` | nil sandbox, zero expiry, success, duplicate |\n327: | `UpdateSandbox()` | nil, not found, success |\n328: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` | success |\n329: | `ListExpiredSandboxes()` | limit <= 0, found, none |\n330: | `ListInactiveSandboxes()` | similar to expired |\n331: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` | empty sessionID, not found, success |\n332: | `Close()` | cleanup |\n333: \n334: ### 6.10 pkg/store/store_valkey.go (P0)\n335: \n336: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n337: |-----------|----------|\n338: | Similar to Redis store tests | |\n339: \n340: ### 6.11 pkg/store/codec.go (P2)\n341: \n342: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n343: |-----------|----------|\n344: | `marshalSandboxInfo()` / `unmarshalSandboxInfo()` | valid/invalid data |\n345: \n346: ### 6.12 pkg/store/singleton.go (P2)\n347: \n348: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n349: |-----------|----------|\n350: | `GetStore()` / `InitStore()` / `CloseStore()` | singleton pattern |\n351: \n352: ### 6.13 pkg/picod/executor.go (P0)\n353: \n354: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n355: |-----------|----------|\n356: | `NewExecutor()` | initialization |\n357: | `Run()` | command not found, timeout, OOM, success |\n358: | `Start()` | similar to Run |\n359: | `limitedBuffer.Write()` / `Bytes()` | within limit, over limit |\n360: \n361: ### 6.14 pkg/picod/security.go (P1)\n362: \n363: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n364: |-----------|----------|\n365: | `ValidateCommand()` | allowed/blocked commands, paths |\n366: \n367: ### 6.15 pkg/picod/limits.go (P1)\n368: \n369: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n370: |-----------|----------|\n371: | `DefaultResourceLimits()` | defaults |\n372: | `Apply()` | set limits on command |\n373: \n374: ### 6.16 pkg/picod/quota.go (P1)\n375: \n376: | 函数/方法 | 测试场景 |\n377: |-----------|----------|\n378: | `DefaultFileQuota()` | defaults |\n379: | `CheckFileSize()` / `CheckTotalSize()` | within/over quota |\n380: \n381: ## 7. Implementation Plan\n382: \n383: ### Phase 1: Router Core (8h)\n384: ```\n385: - [ ] router/router_test.go (补充覆盖)\n386: - [ ] router/handler_test.go (补充覆盖)\n387: - [ ] router/types_test.go\n388: - [ ] router/config_test.go\n389: ```\n390: \n391: ### Phase 2: Router Extended (6h)\n392: ```\n393: - [ ] router/resolver_test.go (补充覆盖)\n394: - [ ] router/health_test.go (补充覆盖)\n395: - [ ] router/session_handler_test.go\n396: - [ ] router/session_resolver_test.go\n397: ```\n398: \n399: ### Phase 3: Router Handlers (4h)\n400: ```\n401: - [ ] router/handlers/token_test.go\n402: - [ ] router/handlers/refresh_test.go\n403: - [ ] router/handlers/revoke_test.go\n404: ```\n405: \n406: ### Phase 4: Router Auth (4h)\n407: ```\n408: - [ ] router/auth/jwt_test.go\n409: - [ ] router/middleware/auth_test.go (补充覆盖)\n410: - [ ] router/middleware/session_middleware_test.go (补充覆盖)\n411: ```\n412: \n413: ### Phase 5: Store (6h)\n414: ```\n415: - [ ] store/store_redis_test.go (补充 mock 测试)\n416: - [ ] store/store_valkey_test.go (补充 mock 测试)\n417: - [ ] store/store_test.go (补充覆盖)\n418: ```\n419: \n420: ### Phase 6: PicoD Supplement (4h)\n421: ```\n422: - [ ] picod/executor_test.go (补充边缘场景)\n423: - [ ] picod/security_test.go (补充覆盖)\n424: - [ ] picod/limits_test.go (补充覆盖)\n425: - [ ] picod/quota_test.go (补充覆盖)\n426: ```\n427: \n428: ### Phase 7: Integration (4h)\n429: ```\n430: - [ ] 运行测试覆盖率：go test -coverprofile=cover.out ./pkg/...\n431: - [ ] 生成覆盖率报告：go tool cover -html=cover.out\n432: - [ ] 确保覆盖率达标\n433: - [ ] 修复 failing tests\n434: ```\n435: \n436: ## 8. Success Criteria\n437: \n438: 1. ✅ 所有新增测试通过\n439: 2. ✅ 整体覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n440: 3. ✅ 核心模块覆盖率 ≥ 85%\n441: 4. ✅ 无数据竞争（`go test -race` 通过）\n442: 5. ✅ 测试可重复运行（无状态污染）\n443: 6. ✅ CI/CD 集成通过\n444: \n445: ## 9. Dependencies\n446: \n447: - Go 1.21+\n448: - Kubernetes client-go v0.34.1\n449: - github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\n450: - github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\n451: - github.com/stretchr/testify (testing)\n452: - github.com/golang/mock (optional, for mocking)\n453: \n454: ## 10. References\n455: \n456: - [Kubernetes Testing Guide](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-testing/testing.md)\n457: - [client-go testing](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go/tree/master/testing)\n458: - [go-redis testing](https://github.com/redis/go-redis/tree/master)\n459: - `pkg/router/design.md` - Router 详细设计文档\n460: - `pkg/picod/design.md` - PicoD 详细设计文档\n461: - `deployment/client-go.md` - client-go 生成代码说明\n\n(End of file - total 461 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## 1. Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，确保代码质量、可维护性和可靠性。\n\n本提案针对 AR-039 需求，覆盖以下核心组件：\n- **Router**: 路由管理、反向代理、健康检查、JWT 认证\n- **Store**: Redis/Valkey 存储后端、会话管理、过期/ inactive 清理\n- **PicoD**: 沙箱执行器、文件系统、资源限制、安全选项\n\n## 2. Scope\n\n### 2.1 In Scope\n\n| 模块 | 文件 | 优先级 | 测试类型 | 当前状态 |\n|------|------|--------|----------|----------|\n| **pkg/router** | | | | |\n| | `router.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 部分覆盖 |\n| | `handler.go` | P0 | 单元测试 | 部分覆盖 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775890277592,"end":1775890277603}}}}
